content.text: Hey, what are you up to today?
Hey! Just moved from VA to PA today. I'm tired but excited about the change.
Nice! I'm from PA originally, but I live in CA now.
I've always wanted to visit California! What's it like there?
It's amazing! The weather is beautiful year-round and there's always something to do.
That sounds amazing! I'm excited to move to Australia in the future.
Oh cool! Why are you moving to Australia?
I've always wanted to live there and I have family there.
That's awesome! I hope you have a great time there.
Thanks! I'm sure I will.
Do you have any hobbies?
I love to sing and I'm also a big fan of rock music.
Me too! What are some of your favorite bands?
I love a lot of different bands, but some of my favorites are AC/DC, Metallica, and Guns N' Roses.
Nice! Those are all great bands. I'm a big fan of AC/DC too.
They're my favorite band! What's your favorite song by them?
I can't choose just one! But I love Back in Black, Highway to Hell, and Thunderstruck.
Those are all great songs! I love Back in Black and Highway to Hell too.
They're so good! I'm glad we have similar music tastes.
Me too! It's always nice to meet someone who likes the same music you do.
Yeah, it is! I'm sure we'll be good friends.
I think so too
